      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>GOLDSTEIN--Charles. Be loved husband of the late Adelaide. Devoted father of Leslie (Franklin) Abrams and Dr. Scott (Nadine) Goldstein. Cherished grandfather of Courtney, Jason, Ross, and Spencer. Loving brother of Mildred Kaminsky, and Jack Goldstein. He was an inspiration to us all and will be in our hearts forever. Services Sunday 10am at Temple Beth-El of Great Neck.</p>
      </block>
